Struct Documentation¶

template<class float_t>
struct collection_model_constants_t¶

Struct to hold model constants for particle collection that we usually are not interested in regarding their influence on the overall model. It is stored within a struct model_constants_t for different collisions such as hail and ice collection or ice and rain riming.
